  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>当前版本已完成的优化和修复：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ 1、移动端适配已完成：现已完成所有苹果4G运存与6G运存手机的适配！从iPhone11至17都能流畅游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ 2、PC端性能优化已经完成：更新优化了运行内存占用、对显卡的性能消耗，1050TI显卡设备现在可以流畅体验了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ 3、BUG修复：已修复完老版本百分之九十的BUG（(如有遗漏还望大家及时联系我们)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏简介】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（“创新工坊”现已推出，当前已更新14个免费玩法资料片）《下一站江湖Ⅱ》是白玉京工作室研发的第二款3D单机武侠游戏，是一款包含了沙盒式的剧情主角养成、无缝大地图任意采集建造模拟经营、骑砍Like式门派霸图玩法的开放世界游戏，无内购、可离网游玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在《下一站江湖Ⅱ》里，各位大侠可以自由闯荡江湖：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 角色扮演（RPG）：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(1) 体验不同主角全新独立的百万字剧情及几十种结局；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(2) 还可以开启数十种市井身份及不同身份独有剧情、规则玩法；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(3) 数百种神功绝学等待收集与搭配，甚至能手搓十八式降龙等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 模拟经营（Sect Builder+SLG）：开启江湖霸图体验不同门派的恩怨情仇、武学套路，模拟经营门派势力城镇矿山药田青楼赌坊等，在大世界一砖一瓦建设起独属于你自己的<strong>天下会、无双城</strong>；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 大型战争（Large-scale wars）体验骑砍like式的门派霸图、武林争霸； </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>未来版本规划</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/0d2679f3a5d5a640544ec7641775edf2.avif?t=1770964110\" width=1200 height=5204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a2ba10050afaee772f908d9a0ac27786.avif?t=1770964110\" width=882 height=2222 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>已完成的版本更新：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/48143b44726909b40ce3b5d713fc455d.avif?t=1770964110\" width=876 height=5488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/8c88b5441895d0228d1752c422fd5d1c.avif?t=1770964110\" width=876 height=4552 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游戏背景】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千年前，从七国争雄，再到三国鼎立。经过数百年和平之后，各国出现不同的问题，夏国兴盛，周国弱小，晋国稳定但无法发展。二十年前，周国皇子宗瑞改革，而晋国章武帝被囚禁。此时，掉阖谷一脉察觉到天下大乱的征兆，夏晋周之间的小型冲突逐渐升级，涉及到信仰归属。最终，以太初剑宗为首的道教、以嵩室山为首的佛教、以砚溪山庄为首的儒教，约定于雁门关论教，预示着天下大变的开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【主角身份】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非固定开局，你可以选择向往江湖的将门大少爷、寒窗十年的木讷书生、踏月留香的江湖浪子，逃婚出走的懵懂大小姐...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游戏特色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可以自由选择不同出生，以不一样的人生去体验这百年盛世！每个出生都是完整独立的全新数十万字剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fdce4fad67d565cb204533084b19522a.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fdce4fad67d565cb204533084b19522a.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fdce4fad67d565cb204533084b19522a.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可使用轻功，草上飞、水上漂、踏浪行波、飞檐走壁。在江湖世界的各个角落尽情探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/420ea3a6d35200b70a10082b47f8d96c.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/420ea3a6d35200b70a10082b47f8d96c.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/420ea3a6d35200b70a10082b47f8d96c.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家也可以游走在主线剧情之外，可自由拜入数十个门派，体验不同门派独有的剧情路线、恩怨情仇、武学流派、规则特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可在大世界里自由收集建造自己的建筑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/88c9a2fb99ffd96793b58d549641ba9d.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/88c9a2fb99ffd96793b58d549641ba9d.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/88c9a2fb99ffd96793b58d549641ba9d.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可以骑砍like的形式争霸江湖</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/36aa200b33c5fde6eab900557880ae73.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/36aa200b33c5fde6eab900557880ae73.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/36aa200b33c5fde6eab900557880ae73.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家还能再江湖里选择数十个不同的市井身份，体验各具特色的身份RPG剧情玩法和规则，以不同的角度笑傲江湖</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a0ba2f83a5fff0c3354c5953f874a55c.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a0ba2f83a5fff0c3354c5953f874a55c.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a0ba2f83a5fff0c3354c5953f874a55c.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>江湖百业：青楼赌坊、朝堂黑市，模拟经营</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/212d99d6ab6acd69da4a4e7100fd9973.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/212d99d6ab6acd69da4a4e7100fd9973.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/212d99d6ab6acd69da4a4e7100fd9973.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>最真实的江湖武学修炼：经脉到功法、招式到内功周天运营，最畅快的武侠养成反馈；天、地、人三界绝学，不入流到一流的各种功法，数千种搭配路线，走出独一无二的大侠之路，并在华山论剑中天下扬名</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/3b760b0a0d5f196fb9285d7dce584e59.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/3b760b0a0d5f196fb9285d7dce584e59.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/3b760b0a0d5f196fb9285d7dce584e59.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/43247b740f0a1380c4f341419aaa9745.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/43247b740f0a1380c4f341419aaa9745.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/43247b740f0a1380c4f341419aaa9745.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种挑战模式：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实江湖、险恶江湖、爽文江湖：从武学到词条，满足不同大侠的追求</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从江湖虾米到独步天下：解锁传奇之路</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/73959beab7ba98abcc97903f9b019c80.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/73959beab7ba98abcc97903f9b019c80.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/73959beab7ba98abcc97903f9b019c80.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MOD编辑器，创新工坊：我们提供这个开放大世界舞台，与大侠们一起打造首款老滚5like的武侠大世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/ec44a15e975924497f9b6c705916b63f.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=572 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/ec44a15e975924497f9b6c705916b63f.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/ec44a15e975924497f9b6c705916b63f.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >庞大内容、及时更新：上线迄今已超过百更、八部大型玩法资料片！2025年我们将继续砥砺前行，用更多更好玩的内容来填充这个江湖大世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，白玉京工作室的所有小伙伴祝大家春节快乐！愿江湖伴你一路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【关注我们】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方微信好友（也可通过它加入下一站江湖II之华山论剑微信群） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/2d2a84f45d00b8bfb934de997113f2e3.avif?t=1770964110\" width=298 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注bilibili: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fb0d94e9ebf92eca40befa77ab356c97.avif?t=1770964110\" width=299 height=299 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——说武、说义、说英雄；谁是英雄？下一站江湖！                   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白玉京工作室 拜上</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>当前版本已完成的优化和修复：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ 1、移动端适配已完成：现已完成所有苹果4G运存与6G运存手机的适配！从iPhone11至17都能流畅游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ 2、PC端性能优化已经完成：更新优化了运行内存占用、对显卡的性能消耗，1050TI显卡设备现在可以流畅体验了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >➤ 3、BUG修复：已修复完老版本百分之九十的BUG（(如有遗漏还望大家及时联系我们)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏简介】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（“创新工坊”现已推出，当前已更新14个免费玩法资料片）《下一站江湖Ⅱ》是白玉京工作室研发的第二款3D单机武侠游戏，是一款包含了沙盒式的剧情主角养成、无缝大地图任意采集建造模拟经营、骑砍Like式门派霸图玩法的开放世界游戏，无内购、可离网游玩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在《下一站江湖Ⅱ》里，各位大侠可以自由闯荡江湖：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 角色扮演（RPG）：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(1) 体验不同主角全新独立的百万字剧情及几十种结局；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(2) 还可以开启数十种市井身份及不同身份独有剧情、规则玩法；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(3) 数百种神功绝学等待收集与搭配，甚至能手搓十八式降龙等</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 模拟经营（Sect Builder+SLG）：开启江湖霸图体验不同门派的恩怨情仇、武学套路，模拟经营门派势力城镇矿山药田青楼赌坊等，在大世界一砖一瓦建设起独属于你自己的<strong>天下会、无双城</strong>；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 大型战争（Large-scale wars）体验骑砍like式的门派霸图、武林争霸； </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>未来版本规划</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/0d2679f3a5d5a640544ec7641775edf2.avif?t=1770964110\" width=1200 height=5204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a2ba10050afaee772f908d9a0ac27786.avif?t=1770964110\" width=882 height=2222 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>已完成的版本更新：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/48143b44726909b40ce3b5d713fc455d.avif?t=1770964110\" width=876 height=5488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/8c88b5441895d0228d1752c422fd5d1c.avif?t=1770964110\" width=876 height=4552 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游戏背景】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >千年前，从七国争雄，再到三国鼎立。经过数百年和平之后，各国出现不同的问题，夏国兴盛，周国弱小，晋国稳定但无法发展。二十年前，周国皇子宗瑞改革，而晋国章武帝被囚禁。此时，掉阖谷一脉察觉到天下大乱的征兆，夏晋周之间的小型冲突逐渐升级，涉及到信仰归属。最终，以太初剑宗为首的道教、以嵩室山为首的佛教、以砚溪山庄为首的儒教，约定于雁门关论教，预示着天下大变的开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【主角身份】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非固定开局，你可以选择向往江湖的将门大少爷、寒窗十年的木讷书生、踏月留香的江湖浪子，逃婚出走的懵懂大小姐...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【游戏特色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可以自由选择不同出生，以不一样的人生去体验这百年盛世！每个出生都是完整独立的全新数十万字剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fdce4fad67d565cb204533084b19522a.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fdce4fad67d565cb204533084b19522a.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fdce4fad67d565cb204533084b19522a.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可使用轻功，草上飞、水上漂、踏浪行波、飞檐走壁。在江湖世界的各个角落尽情探索</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/420ea3a6d35200b70a10082b47f8d96c.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/420ea3a6d35200b70a10082b47f8d96c.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/420ea3a6d35200b70a10082b47f8d96c.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家也可以游走在主线剧情之外，可自由拜入数十个门派，体验不同门派独有的剧情路线、恩怨情仇、武学流派、规则特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可在大世界里自由收集建造自己的建筑</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/88c9a2fb99ffd96793b58d549641ba9d.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/88c9a2fb99ffd96793b58d549641ba9d.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/88c9a2fb99ffd96793b58d549641ba9d.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家可以骑砍like的形式争霸江湖</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/36aa200b33c5fde6eab900557880ae73.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/36aa200b33c5fde6eab900557880ae73.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/36aa200b33c5fde6eab900557880ae73.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>玩家还能再江湖里选择数十个不同的市井身份，体验各具特色的身份RPG剧情玩法和规则，以不同的角度笑傲江湖</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a0ba2f83a5fff0c3354c5953f874a55c.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a0ba2f83a5fff0c3354c5953f874a55c.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/a0ba2f83a5fff0c3354c5953f874a55c.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>江湖百业：青楼赌坊、朝堂黑市，模拟经营</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/212d99d6ab6acd69da4a4e7100fd9973.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/212d99d6ab6acd69da4a4e7100fd9973.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/212d99d6ab6acd69da4a4e7100fd9973.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>最真实的江湖武学修炼：经脉到功法、招式到内功周天运营，最畅快的武侠养成反馈；天、地、人三界绝学，不入流到一流的各种功法，数千种搭配路线，走出独一无二的大侠之路，并在华山论剑中天下扬名</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/3b760b0a0d5f196fb9285d7dce584e59.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/3b760b0a0d5f196fb9285d7dce584e59.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/3b760b0a0d5f196fb9285d7dce584e59.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/43247b740f0a1380c4f341419aaa9745.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/43247b740f0a1380c4f341419aaa9745.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/43247b740f0a1380c4f341419aaa9745.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种挑战模式：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实江湖、险恶江湖、爽文江湖：从武学到词条，满足不同大侠的追求</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从江湖虾米到独步天下：解锁传奇之路</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/73959beab7ba98abcc97903f9b019c80.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/73959beab7ba98abcc97903f9b019c80.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/73959beab7ba98abcc97903f9b019c80.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MOD编辑器，创新工坊：我们提供这个开放大世界舞台，与大侠们一起打造首款老滚5like的武侠大世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/ec44a15e975924497f9b6c705916b63f.poster.avif?t=1770964110\" width=572 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/ec44a15e975924497f9b6c705916b63f.webm?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/ec44a15e975924497f9b6c705916b63f.mp4?t=1770964110\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >庞大内容、及时更新：上线迄今已超过百更、八部大型玩法资料片！2025年我们将继续砥砺前行，用更多更好玩的内容来填充这个江湖大世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后，白玉京工作室的所有小伙伴祝大家春节快乐！愿江湖伴你一路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【关注我们】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方微信好友（也可通过它加入下一站江湖II之华山论剑微信群） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/2d2a84f45d00b8bfb934de997113f2e3.avif?t=1770964110\" width=298 height=298 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注bilibili: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1606180/extras/fb0d94e9ebf92eca40befa77ab356c97.avif?t=1770964110\" width=299 height=299 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >——说武、说义、说英雄；谁是英雄？下一站江湖！                   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白玉京工作室 拜上</p>",
